-05-24T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4e3f2e7bc683c530070d341e96caaaa7d25efd7","tid":2030591,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff1e7f1b4f698333ef1e9717ec5c8dea8170b9e","tid":2030591,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"33cf7f0cb81865a23953fa51cb3b1a9ba9e2f4fe","tid":2030591,"uid":302829,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:23:27.000Z","msg":"真係cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部獨post都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8